<L>__{interior stairway}
<A>__{he takes the steps two at a time, pulling the stocking down over his face as he reaches the top and bursts through the open door leading into}
<L>__{interior joppy's bar}
<A>__{he charges through the raucous laughter of the half full room right up to the bar. joppy nearly drops the glasses he is clearing away as he looks down the barrel of the pistol aimed at his face.}
<C>__{easy}
<D>__{come on, joppy. let's go!}
<A>__{joppy hesitates, recognizing the voice.}
<C>__{easy}
<D>__{you heard me. i will blow your head off!}
<A>__{and he cocks the hammer, causing joppy to get a move on from behind the bar. easy shoves him through the door, calling back to the startled crowd on his way out.}
<C>__{easy}
<D>__{don't follow me, goddammit!}
<A>__{and he's gone.}
